,"body":"As with Microsoft SQL Server there is no default sortorder when sorting `text` fields. But sorting for the first n characters does work.\n\nThis is the table:\n\n```\nCREATE TABLE [comments] (\n[id] INT IDENTITY(1, 1),\n[comment] TEXT DEFAULT '',\nPRIMARY KEY ([id])\n);\n```\n\nSo, this Query works:\n\n```\nSELECT \"id\", \"comment\" FROM \"comments\" ORDER BY SUBSTRING(comment, 1, 45) ASC\n```\n\nw/ CI's `query()`method, it does work too:\n\n```\n$this->db->query('SELECT \"id\", \"comment\" FROM \"comments\" ORDER BY SUBSTRING(comment, 1, 45) ASC');\n```\n\nBut using the `order_by()` method causes trouble:\n\n```\n// $this->db->select('id, comment', FALSE);\n$this->db->select('id, comment');\n// $this->db->order_by('SUBSTRING(comment, 1, 45)', 'ASC');\n$this->db->order_by('SUBSTRING(comment, 1, 45) ASC');\n$this->db->get('comments');\n```\n\nError message:\n\n```\nError Number: 42000/156\n[Microsoft][SQL Server Native Client 11.0][SQL Server]Incorrect syntax near the keyword 'ASC'.\nSELECT \"id\", \"comment\" FROM \"comments\" ORDER BY SUBSTRING(comment, 1, \"45)\" ASC\n```\n\nI suggest to add an optional parameter for the `order_by()`method for not being magical ;) so the `ORDER BY` part won't be touched.\n","closed_by":{"login":"narfbg","id":1058011,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjEwNTgwMTE=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1058011?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg","html_url":"https://github.com/narfbg","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/bcit-ci/CodeIgniter/issues/1925/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/bcit-ci/CodeIgniter/issues/1925/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":"completed"}